To perform setup run the following.

on osx install macports then add the following to the .bash_profile
export PATH=/opt/local/bin:$PATH

sudo gem install soloist

git clone git@github.com:ledona/delano_setup.git
cd delano_setup
git submodule init
git submodule update

---- Then for the full setup run
soloist

---- For just emacs run
soloist workstation::emacs

----
Emacs >=24 required for all the emacs goodness